videos.headline: Warren gets Cincinnati on the board with 24-yd TD run
videos.description: Cincinnati's Michael Warren runs 24 yards into the end zone for a touchdown to cut into Temple's lead.

videos.headline: Temple scores first TD of game through air
videos.description: Anthony Russo finds Randle Jones for a 16-yard Temple touchdown to jump ahead of Cincinnati.

videos.headline: McClelland gives Bearcats first lead of game
videos.description: Charles McClelland bolts down the field for a 42-yard touchdown run, giving Cincinnati their first lead of the game.

videos.headline: Cincinnati punter boots 72-yard punt
videos.description: Cincinnati's James Smith flips the field on Temple with a 72-yard punt.

videos.headline: Temple ties game late with 20-yd TD pass
videos.description: Anthony Russo connects with Branden Mack for a 20-yard Owls touchdown.

videos.headline: Temple strikes first in OT with 25-yd TD
videos.description: Anthony Russo finds Isaiah Wright for a 25-yard Temple touchdown.
